+@captain
+Feature: Tide prediction edge cases
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Time zone handling consistency
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T04:10:00Z"
+    Then the predicted high tide should handle UTC timezone consistently
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Exact time match edge case
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T16:45:00Z"
+    Then the predicted high tide should be after the exact match time
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Invalid input handling
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "invalid-date-string"
+    Then the prediction should handle invalid input gracefully
